quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  20,77,"Gom…óii Men wahaynii faade e Muusaa ro∆¥idu e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen wa…óan …ìe laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wata a hulu hewtiteede wata a hulu [yoolagol]"
